        {
            "title": "美伊會談｜美伊於周六舉行會談 前設海峽保持開放 白宮：伊朗方案不能接受",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"500\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/HCuOiXdKqsDl6uBB48fy7A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwNQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bossmind_356/bd96629b11a2b50bd310429be36ca9e3\" width=\"950\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">白宮發言人<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"萊維特\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:萊維特;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/萊維特\">萊維特</a>表示美伊將於星期六舉行會談，美方要求談判的前提是<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"霍爾木茲海峽\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:霍爾木茲海峽;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/霍爾木茲海峽\">霍爾木茲海峽</a>保持開放，並表示早前流出的伊朗「10點方案」已經被完全否決。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">萊維特在記者會上表示，雙方會談將會在巴基斯坦伊斯蘭堡舉行，美方代表團將由萬斯率領，團隊成員包括總統特使威特科夫及特朗普的女婿庫什納。對於伊朗提出的「10點方案」，當中條款包括美國接受伊朗擁有濃縮油的權利，美方表示有關要求完全不能接受，伊朗停止提煉濃縮鈾仍是特朗普的「紅線」，一直沒有改變。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-0b81d284-9170-3fed-acc7-4fbf13a847ae-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">萊維特表示伊朗提出另一份「更合理、內容完全不同更簡明」的方案，雙方會談將以新方案的基礎作為談判基礎，表明停火期間美軍不會立即撤走，並將保持戰備狀態。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">伊朗外長阿拉格齊早前表示，若果針對伊朗的攻擊停止，伊朗將會同意停課火，並宣布霍爾木茲海峽將可安全通航，為期兩周。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%83%E8%AB%87-%E7%BE%8E%E4%BC%8A%E6%96%BC%E5%91%A8%E5%85%AD%E8%88%89%E8%A1%8C%E6%9C%83%E8%AB%87-%E5%89%8D%E8%A8%AD%E6%B5%B7%E5%B3%BD%E4%BF%9D%E6%8C%81%E9%96%8B%E6%94%BE-%E7%99%BD%E5%AE%AE-%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97-050927459.html",
